From 4007ff3b44269d2f48e5aa938cf621fbd0123df9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Bogdan Pintea <bogdan.pintea@elastic.co>
Date: Thu, 19 Dec 2024 17:58:06 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] ESQL: allow DATE_PARSE to read the timezones (#118603)

This just removes fixing a formatter to a timezone (UTC), allowing
`DATE_PARSE` to correctly read timezones.

Fixes #117680.
